feedback: SYVK is a yoga center par excellence. The instructors are experienced and are knowledgeable. If you're looking to improve your health, SYVK is the place to be. Guddad Sir's class is liberating and has a soothing effect. It's been a little over a month, my stress level has reduced and I've almost regained my flexibility. The class timings are convenient. The morning classes start at 5 AM while the evening classes are from 4 PM to 8 PM. If you have a desk job and stress has taken toll on your health, you most certainly need to enroll here.
